Interface StringConverter<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AmountConverter, FileParameterType, StringConverterFactory.BooleanConverter, StringConverterFactory.ByteConverter, StringConverterFactory.DoubleConverter, StringConverterFactory.FloatConverter, StringConverterFactory.IntConverter, StringConverterFactory.LongConverter, StringConverterFactory.ShortConverter, StringConverterFactory.StringStringConverter

    public interface StringConverter<T>
    Converts an Object to and from a String representation. Subclasses are specialized for specified objects.
    Author:
    Nick Collier

    • Method Summary

      Creates an Object from a String representation.
